name: Oxblood Leather Tote
description:
This is the perfect tote bag. With enough space for a laptop, books, a wallet, sunglasses, and any other daily essentials, the bag features one interior pocket and an interior strap to keep tall items upright or to hang sunglasses on. The bag is made from oxblood leather that will break in beautifully and will darken over time.

- Made in the USA
- Riveted details.
- 17" x 16".
- Interior Pocket with flap closure
- Adjustable Handles 
- Includes Monogrammed Key Fob 
- Hand Sewn

name: Card Sleeve - Oxblood
description: The card sleeve is our slimmest cardholder.  Hand cut and sewn of an oiled utility leather, the sleeve is sized perfectly to hold business cards, or credit cards and a few folded bills.  The design is a great way to stay minimal while looking put together.  Holds up to a dozen cards.  Measurements:  3” x 3.75”

name: Deluxe Key Fob - Oxblood
description: Clipped onto your belt loop or secured to a bag strap, this key fob will keep your keys collected. The oiled utility leather will break in over time, and consistent use will create a wear pattern specific to the way you use and wear it. The trigger clasp is both sturdy and easy to use. The top key-ring adds versatility but is removable via the snap closure.  All hardware is nickel-plated.

name: iPad Envelope Case
description: This is the best iPad case ever. It is made out of one piece of oily utility leather that scratches up beautifully over time as it protects your iPad. The case closes with a distressed button stud that is easy to open or fasten with the flick of a hand. Don't worry, there is a layer of leather between the metal and the iPad so that nothing will scratch the screen. There is a hidden interior space to hold a stylus or pen, and an exterior space that can hold a cell phone, wallet, or whatever else you want to put in there.
